1. *Svetog* Nikolu slavimo svake godine u decembru. (We celebrate *St.* Nicholas every year in December.)
2. Danas sam posetio *svetu* Goru u Grčkoj. (Today, I visited *the Holy* Mountain in Greece.)
3. U našoj crkvi se nalazi ikona *svetog* Jovana. (In our church, there is an icon of *St.* John.)
4. Njegov *sveti* krst je bio nasleđe porodice. (His *holy* cross was a family inheritance.)
5. Želim da posetim *sveta* mesta u Jerusalimu. (I want to visit *holy* places in Jerusalem.)
6. *Sveti* arhanđeo Mihailo je poznat u hrišćanskoj veri. (The *Saint* Archangel Michael is well-known in Christian faith.)
7. Uvek mi je drago da vidim *svetog* Petra kad idem u Vatikan. (I'm always happy to see *St.* Peter when I go to the Vatican.)
8. Naši preci su verovali da im *sveti* Sava pomaže u teškim trenucima. (Our ancestors believed that *St.* Sava helped them in difficult times.)
9. *Svetom* Martinu se posvećuje jedan od najpoznatijih festivala vina u Francuskoj. (One of the most famous wine festivals in France is dedicated to *St.* Martin.)
10. Ovde se nalazi grob *svetog* Luke, jednog od apostola. (Here is the tomb of *St.* Luke, one of the apostles.)